---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Statistics">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Statistics</p>
      <h1>Platform overview.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Key metrics for the My MetaTrader protocol. Figures are approximate and update on-chain.
      </p>
      <div class="grid stats-grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>Max leverage</h3><p>Up to 1000x on major crypto and forex pairs.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Execution model</h3><p>No scam wick protection with transparent on-chain settlement.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Vault yield</h3><p>Real yield from trading fees, not inflationary emissions.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Custody</h3><p>Non-custodial. You keep control of your wallet and funds at all times.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Availability</h3><p>24/7 markets with no maintenance windows or withdrawal freezes.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Transparency</h3><p>All trades and liquidations are verifiable on-chain.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .stats-grid {
    margin-top: 42px;
  }
</style>
